00:45:46,702 --> 00:45:50,002
Thank you all so much for coming to...

83
00:45:52,702 --> 00:45:57,802
...Takanashi Kiara and Ninomae Ina'nis's first concert, Drawn to Dawn!

84
00:45:57,802 --> 00:46:01,202
Ki... Thank you, thank you.

85
00:46:01,202 --> 00:46:04,402
Ki-ki-ri-ki!

86
00:46:05,702 --> 00:46:08,702
I am Takanashi Kiara, and...

87
00:46:09,002 --> 00:46:15,702
Good morning, afternoon, evening, everyone! It's Ninomae Ina'nis!

88
00:46:16,402 --> 00:46:22,702
That's right, it's finally time for our concert! Is everyone hyped?

89
00:46:25,702 --> 00:46:32,202
Before we kick things off, we have some important safety rules and house guidelines to go over.

90
00:46:32,502 --> 00:46:40,202
First, photography and the use of any recording equipment are strictly prohibited during the performance.

91
00:46:40,502 --> 00:46:45,502
Also, the venue is smoke-free, so please refrain from smoking inside.

92
00:46:46,702 --> 00:46:50,202
But what... But what if I'm smoking hot?

93
00:46:50,202 --> 00:46:52,202
Oh, Kiara...

94
00:46:54,202 --> 00:47:02,702
If you start feeling unwell at any point, please don't push yourself. Just reach out to the nearest staff member for help, and hydrate!

95
00:47:03,402 --> 00:47:08,202
For everyone's safety, please avoid any dangerous or disruptive behavior.

96
00:47:08,202 --> 00:47:11,702
This includes moshing...

97
00:47:11,702 --> 00:47:14,702
No moshing, I mean it!

98
00:47:14,702 --> 00:47:22,702
Moshing, diving, sitting on shoulders, jumping excessively, or throwing objects towards the stage.

99
00:47:23,002 --> 00:47:30,202
Climbing onto the stage, intentionally blocking the aisles, or rushing toward the front is also (surprise!) not allowed.

100
00:47:30,702 --> 00:47:39,402
Please refrain from disruptive shouting, erratic lightstick movements, or any extreme motions that might interfere with the experience of those around you. Be considerate!

101
00:47:40,002 --> 00:47:46,502
If you don't follow the instructions of our staff or the venue staff, you may be asked to leave the venue.

102
00:47:48,502 --> 00:48:01,002
Yes, please keep in mind that the venue organizers, performers, and staff cannot be held responsible for any accidents, equipment damage, or trouble caused by failing to follow instructions.

103
00:48:01,502 --> 00:48:12,702
Additionally, any costs for damages resulting from ignoring these rules will be the responsibility of the person involved, so be careful, guys, okay?

104
00:48:13,702 --> 00:48:20,702
There are cameras in the venue for filming and photography today, and you might appear in footage or photos.

105
00:48:20,702 --> 00:48:26,702
These may be used for promotional purposes later on, so please keep that in mind.

106
00:48:28,702 --> 00:48:34,402
And finally... big news! Today's concert will be in two parts!

107
00:48:34,402 --> 00:48:41,202
There's a part for Kiara and a part for me, so please look forward to both of them!

108
00:48:43,702 --> 00:48:51,702
All right! That is it for the rules. The show is about to begin, so get ready!

109
00:48:52,002 --> 00:48:53,502
Bye-bye!

110
00:48:53,502 --> 00:48:55,202
Bye-bye! See you!

