168
00:58:06,745 --> 00:58:10,245
嫌い嫌いの最低泣いてダウン
I hate it, it's the worst—I burst into tears and I'm down

169
00:58:19,945 --> 00:58:23,245
毎度新たにお願い1つ
Every time, I have one new wish...

170
00:58:23,245 --> 00:58:26,545
愛も変わらずピックアップのワーニング ワーニング
The same love as ever, plus a picked-up warning, warning

