179
01:01:26,763 --> 01:01:31,763
Kikiriki! Welcome to Day 1 of Drawn to Dawn!

180
01:01:31,763 --> 01:01:35,763
I am Takanashi Kiara. Let's kick it off!

181
01:01:36,563 --> 01:01:40,763
瞬く 星の降り立つ
The twinkling stars landing...

182
01:01:40,763 --> 01:01:45,263
欠けたステップを繋ぎ合わせた
...piecing together the chipped steps...

183
01:01:45,263 --> 01:01:48,463
メモリー
...into a memory.

184
01:01:48,463 --> 01:01:52,763
聖なる従者が集う
Where the holy servants gather,

185
01:01:52,763 --> 01:01:56,263
神話の理
the principles of myth,

186
01:01:56,263 --> 01:01:59,563
祈りに耳を澄ませ
listen closely to the prayers.

187
01:01:59,563 --> 01:02:02,763
Tell me, I can hear it clearly

188
01:02:02,763 --> 01:02:05,263
Tell me, 声なき声に
Tell me, to the voiceless voice,

189
01:02:05,263 --> 01:02:08,763
あらがう言葉
the words that resist,

190
01:02:08,763 --> 01:02:12,763
導く鼓動が呼ぶ
the guiding heartbeat calls.

191
01:02:12,763 --> 01:02:18,263
ほむら降り注ぐ空に 身を焦がして
Burning my body in the sky where flames pour down,

192
01:02:18,263 --> 01:02:23,663
乱れた空が描いた イミテーション
an imitation drawn by the chaotic sky.

193
01:02:23,663 --> 01:02:29,263
数多重なる試練も生き抜いてみせる
I will survive even the many trials that pile up.

194
01:02:29,263 --> 01:02:35,263
I will live to keep on fighting till the dawn

195
01:02:35,763 --> 01:02:37,263
Oi! Oi! Oi! Oi!

196
01:02:37,263 --> 01:02:38,763
Louder!

197
01:02:40,263 --> 01:02:42,763
Oi! Oi! Oi! Oi!

198
01:02:45,263 --> 01:02:48,763
数えれば先の見えない
With an invisible future...

199
01:02:48,763 --> 01:02:54,763
ゼロの境界 迷い込んだとしても
...even if I wander into the border of zero...

200
01:02:54,763 --> 01:02:59,263
何度も繰り返される 孤独の終焉
...the end of loneliness repeated over and over,

201
01:02:59,263 --> 01:03:06,763
そこに残ったアンサー
the answer left there.

202
01:03:07,763 --> 01:03:10,763
Don't break, we will never give up

203
01:03:10,763 --> 01:03:13,763
Don't break, 羽ばたくそして
Don't break, and then flap my wings,

204
01:03:13,763 --> 01:03:20,463
